ofxGSTT is an openFrameworks addon / wrapper to the inofficial google speech to text api

first version should be ready this weekend

Credits:
it is ported from the processing library by Florian Schulz (http://stt.getflourish.com/)
which is based on Mike Pultz article (http://mikepultz.com/2011/03/accessing-google-speech-api-chrome-11/)
that shows how to use the technologie offered by Google without a browser
